List of User IDs Following Activity

These fields are being automatically populated by a hook. The only reason these fields exist is because REDCap has not yet added functionality to address individual instances in a repeating series, so we cannot use the email trigger to send reminders to only those regions that have not completed a vote by the due date. This feature is in the REDCap roadplan, but not yet implemented as of July 2018. This is a workaround solution.
